{"ok":true,"plugin":"twitter","account":"111","count":2}
[HTTP 200]
### 3. sync twitter acct 222 (twid=u%3D222) -> SECOND jar (no clobber)

POST /api/cookies
{"ok":true,"plugin":"twitter","account":"222","count":2}
[HTTP 200]
